        "timestamp": "2020-05-30 08:11:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> where does this requirement come from?\n> Is it a LF IT need to save some resources during CI operations?\n> when we build our xtesting dockers we clone also with this option but this test dockers are ephemeral\n> for a deployment it can be convenient to keep some history sometimes\n> We also need to avoid creating monster repo\n> In Integration we started in frankfurt to reorganize the repo structure to avoid that one repo hosts everything\n> the siez is then more reasonable and the clone time also\n> \n> anyway your change introduced linter errors (rst and vagrant lintting error)\n\nYes, this patch is intended for optimization purpose.\n\nOptimization will come in many forms like :-\n\nless clone time and size results in less build time and less size in all case or specially in docker container size",
        "patchset_number": 2
