        "timestamp": "2020-06-02 11:50:53.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI am still not clear on the source of the need, I found the JIRA but did not find any requirement\nit has never been discussed in my project, so it is a request from LF to save resources?\n\nif so I think that the history is not the main problem regarding the size of the repositories.\nif it would be easy to create repositories, we would have more small repositories and not few monster ones used as shared drive that could be long to clone\n\nIn your patch, you looked for all the instances, in the use case documentation (rst) It will not save anything.\non  bootstrap and deployment, why not, but today the full deployments are not done from here in CI so it will not save time (and money) on Vexxhost here AFAI",
